name: AVAudioQuality
desc: The values that specify the sample rate audio quality for encoding and conversion.

items.name: case min
items.desc: A value that represents a minimum audio quality for encoding and conversion.

items.name: case low
items.desc: A value that represents a low audio quality for encoding and conversion.

items.name: case medium
items.desc: A value that represents a medium audio quality for encoding and conversion.

items.name: case high
items.desc: A value that represents a high audio quality for encoding and conversion.

items.name: case max
items.desc: A value that represents a maximum audio quality for encoding and conversion.
